rmer Title 41 by striking out subsec. (c), redesignating subsec. (e) as (c)(1), and adding subsec. (c)(2)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idd107fe79-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"idd107fe7a-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Nonapplicability of National Emergencies Act","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The provisions of the National Emergencies Act [see Short Title note set out under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s1601"},"text":"section 1601 of this title","children":[],"tail":"] shall not apply to the powers and authorities conferred by this section and actions taken hereunder, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s1651/a/4"},"text":"section 1651(a)(4) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
